Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Conan Episode 1038 "Police Academy \NArc Wild Police Story CASE. Date Wataru"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,[op]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,[ed]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,CULPRIT A,0000,0000,0000,,[eyecatch]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.62,0:00:06.09,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,By one month after entering the academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.09,0:00:09.54,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,the students have grown accustomed \Nto life at the police academy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:14.40,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,and are finally permitted to leave \Nthe academy and stay out overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:23.76,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Onizuka's class, keep those hands moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:26.54,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this place cleaned \Nup quick so we can eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:27.76,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:30.00,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.92,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Could you lend me your dustpan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:33.21,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:36.51,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,But you'd better Rei-turn it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:39.26,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic. Two points.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:41.89,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you mean zero points?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:46.10,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Those two have become fast friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:50.40,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,As Jinpei-chan's best friend, \NI'm a little jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:52.11,DCMain,FEMALE STUDENT A,0000,0000,0000,,Hagiwara-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:55.29,DCMain,FEMALE STUDENT A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget we've got a \Nmixer on our next day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.29,0:00:57.36,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.77,0:01:00.21,DCMain,FEMALE STUDENT A,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you bring a bunch of hot guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:03.25,DCMain,FEMALE STUDENT B,0000,0000,0000,,Like that blond foreigner over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:05.25,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:07.25,DCMain,FEMALE STUDENT B,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:08.71,DCMain,FEMALE STUDENT A,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:10.71,DCMain,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:13.91,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Tomori Cleaning here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.77,0:01:17.13,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to collect your uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:19.51,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry they're always so sweaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:20.75,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.75,0:01:24.02,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Someday you'll be protecting us citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.87,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a small price to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.68,0:01:29.36,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It comes to visit after falling asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:31.49,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Fall in love with logical deduction \Nand the pleasure of solving mysteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:32.75,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Their youth is in full bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:34.84,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The bond between Amuro and \Nhis friends will never fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:36.49,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Always determining the one truth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:38.26,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,with the body of a child \Nand the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:40.74,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,his name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:28.97,DCEpTitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(399,1)}Police Academy Arc Wild Police Story \NCASE. Date Wataru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:28.16,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,"Police Academy Arc Wild Police \NStory CASE. Date Wataru!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:33.36,DCMain,MALE STUDENT A,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I haven't prepared for English class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:36.11,DCMain,MALE STUDENT A,0000,0000,0000,,That English teacher really hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.27,DCMain,MALE STUDENT A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared they'll call on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:40.53,DCMain,MALE STUDENT B,0000,0000,0000,,Then get Furuya to teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:42.17,DCMain,MALE STUDENT B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Furuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:45.15,DCMain,MALE STUDENT B,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you'd be fluent in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:46.91,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:49.41,DCMain,MALE STUDENT B,0000,0000,0000,,Figures since you're blond and half.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.68,DCMain,MALE STUDENT B,0000,0000,0000,,I bet your English is better \Nthan the instructor's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:52.33,DCMain,MALE STUDENT B,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:55.83,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't make assumptions about \Npeople based on their appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:56.96,DCMain,MALE STUDENT B,0000,0000,0000,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:57.84,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:02.22,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Quit trying to look cool \Nby chewing on a toothpick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.60,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.22,DCMain,MALE STUDENT B,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:08.31,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.89,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Just be careful from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:14.19,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Team Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:18.23,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Have you got a crush on Furuya-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.80,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,You were oddly defensive of him \Nwhile we were cleaning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:22.92,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:25.16,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.28,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:30.66,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously not. I've got a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:31.56,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:33.66,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:36.23,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:41.17,DCItalic,NATALIE,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:44.77,DCItalic,NATALIE,0000,0000,0000,,You told your police \Nacademy friends about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:47.55,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it just came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:57.77,DCItalic - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,Neat and Tidy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:52.84,DCItalic,NATALIE,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. We promised to keep it a secret \Nuntil we could meet each other's parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:54.19,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:56.86,DCItalic,NATALIE,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ask your dad about his schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.92,DCItalic,NATALIE,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to meet him \Nsooner rather than later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:01.02,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,We can ignore my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:03.56,DCItalic,NATALIE,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:07.32,DCItalic,NATALIE,0000,0000,0000,,So, how's the academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.16,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:13.95,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,There's a combative guy, a flashy playboy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:19.17,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,a guy who's normally calm but secretly \Nresearching something like crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:24.26,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,and a guy like you who attracts a lot of \Nattention just because he looks a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:27.82,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's so interesting, I'm never bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:31.53,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce you to them sometime, Natalie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.94,DCMain,NATALIE,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:40.27,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Arresting techniques are based \Non ancient Japanese martial arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:46.28,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,These techniques were developed for \Narresting suspects and criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:50.72,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,The most effective targets are the \Nchin, shoulder, body, and hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:55.79,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Methods include jabs, kicks, joint \Nlocks, throws, chokes, holds,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:59.79,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,police batons, police sticks, \Nand handcuffs. Anything goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.90,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,The most important part \Nof arresting techniques...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:06.42,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,...is bringing your target under control \Nwithout harming them or yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:11.14,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Ippon! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:17.18,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:20.35,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, the team leader's crazy strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:23.77,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. I could beat him \Nin an ordinary fistfight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:27.24,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm better with women and cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:30.11,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,But the team leader apparently \Nhas a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.99,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't we go somewhere \Nthis weekend to change our luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:40.17,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, as long as it's a car or bike \Nshop and not a machine parts store.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.88,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going somewhere, I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.14,0:06:43.82,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:46.30,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you want to go, \Na car shop or a bike shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.05,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:51.93,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of bike shops, I saw a guy \Nwith a strange tattoo the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:53.43,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,A strange tattoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:56.70,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like a cup with a fancy base.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.06,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's called a goblet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:06:59.92,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of design.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:04.37,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,What was he like? Where does \Nhe live? What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:05.69,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:08.09,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you, Morofushi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:10.74,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:14.91,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so interested, why don't \Nwe go to that bike shop tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:16.66,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Ippon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:18.48,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,He's beaten ten guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:20.62,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Furuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:21.55,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:26.84,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Now this'll be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:31.32,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Furuya's grades are better, but \Nwho knows how this will turn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:32.83,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Get him, Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:35.06,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let lover boy beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:36.39,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:39.81,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:45.90,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hagi. Wanna bet on the winner?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:49.11,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet a yakisoba roll from the \Nacademy store on Zero winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:51.40,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll bet a melon \Nroll on the team captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:54.21,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,He'll beat him. He's on a roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:58.04,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,No, the team captain injured his \Nknee in his match against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:08:00.48,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Zero wouldn't overlook that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:01.91,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,You filthy cheater.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:14.11,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:15.41,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.18,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,That yakisoba roll is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:20.28,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Bringing your opponent under control unharmed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:23.19,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,only applies if you actually \Nbring him under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:25.69,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disappointed in you, Furuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:31.32,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you hit my knee?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.69,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you hesitate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:36.45,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,If this were the real world, \Nyou'd be badly injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:38.95,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,and the suspect would be fleeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:42.57,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Mercy doesn't get you anywhere \Nwith dangerous criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:45.11,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Show any weakness, and you're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.33,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,They'll take full advantage of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:51.34,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,All that's waiting for you is the \Nsame terrible fate my dad suffered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:56.43,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you're stronger than everyone \Nelse, you can't carry out justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:02.85,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:18.19,DCItalic,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you're stronger than everyone \Nelse, you can't carry out justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:23.66,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:24.59,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Zero—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:26.37,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. Were you asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:30.40,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just lying down and thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.13,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:34.51,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to head out with \NMatsuda and Hagiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:36.84,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.62,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:39.26,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:41.57,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have bothered you, Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:42.27,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:45.10,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:48.65,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to the convenience store, \Ncould you get me some toothpaste?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:52.27,DCItalic,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,They're already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:55.80,DCItalic,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I'll go out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.79,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Team Captain Date?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:12.29,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Furuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:17.55,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this afternoon at the dojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:19.27,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,I went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:20.18,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:25.24,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's got nothing to do with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:28.50,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't your dad a police officer, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:29.19,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:31.72,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,He was a patrol officer \Nassigned to a police box.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:35.06,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,He was skinny and looked weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:37.19,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,but I respected him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:41.15,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Until that day my dad was off duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:45.83,DCItalic,YOUNG DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad. Why do you always \Nchew on toothpicks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:49.62,DCItalic,DATE DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Your old man's skinny and \Ndoesn't look very reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:53.59,DCItalic,DATE DAD,0000,0000,0000,,I chew on these so bad guys \Nwon't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:56.39,DCItalic,YOUNG DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Then buy me some toothpicks, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:10:59.38,DCItalic,DATE DAD,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to make do with candy on a stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:02.14,DCItalic,YOUNG DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:04.11,DCItalic,DATE DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:09.06,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,It happened right after \Nmy dad entered the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.70,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,An agitated man covered \Nin someone else's blood
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:16.07,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,came running in with a wooden sword \Nin one hand and demanded money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:20.57,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, there was panic inside \Nthe store, but I wasn't scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:25.82,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,He was just one guy. I knew my dad, the \Npolice officer, would do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:28.70,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,I had total faith in him, \Nbut what I saw was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:33.46,DCItalic,DATE DAD,0000,0000,0000,,You can have my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:36.04,DCItalic,DATE DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Take mine and spare the other customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:39.92,DCItalic,YOUNG DATE,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's a police officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.26,DCItalic,YOUNG DATE,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:46.32,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,My words were like oil on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:50.77,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,The man swung his wooden sword \Ndown on my dad over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:57.41,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually we heard the sound of sirens, \Nand the man left the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:12:01.26,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,But my dad ended up in \Nthe hospital for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:05.34,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,He ended up quitting the force \Nbecause of his injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:11.66,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,I learned later that the \Nman was a gang member
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:14.54,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,who lost a dispute and was \Nlooking for getaway money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:19.21,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently he caused injuries \Nat another store after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:25.05,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, if my dad had been \Nstrong and arrested that man there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:30.78,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,justice would've been carried out \Nwithout producing a single victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:35.60,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you listen to my nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.00,DCMain,CULPRIT A,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody make a sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.85,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why can't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:12.89,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,That guy with the goblet tattoo \Nis a regular here, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:16.19,DCMain,MONOBE,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:21.41,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Morofushi. Tell him why \Nyou're looking for that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:25.62,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Because... Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:33.45,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Morofushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:39.31,DCMain,MONOBE,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go sharing my customers' \Npersonal information without a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:44.46,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, he forgot why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:45.50,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't tell us—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:48.10,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:49.13,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:54.14,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,You know, didn't the team leader say \Nsomething at the dojo about his dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:54.89,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:59.70,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid, I saw a guy \Nwith eyebrows like his get beaten
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:04.19,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,by a yakuza-looking guy \Nat a convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:08.20,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Hagi, tell me more about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:10.82,DCMain,CULPRIT B,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, quit stalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:14.90,DCMain,CULPRIT B,0000,0000,0000,,Put your phones in the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:16.35,DCMain,HOSTAGE,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.39,DCMain,CULPRIT A,0000,0000,0000,,Is that everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.39,0:14:22.28,DCMain,CULPRIT B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:23.84,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Furuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:25.33,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,There are two culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:29.22,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,If you and I handle one of them \Neach, we can take them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:34.83,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,I'll draw the attention of the guy in the \Nbeanie. While he's distracting, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:32.54,DCMain,CULPRIT B,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, this phone is a brand new model.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:36.43,DCMain,CULPRIT A,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You idiot, we'll be able to buy whatever \Nwe want once we finish this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:35.60,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:38.15,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:43.17,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't they stealing the money in \Nthe register and fleeing immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:44.27,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:49.15,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,But rescuing all the customers \Nhere right now is our top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:53.76,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't been tied up \Nyet. Now's our best chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.91,DCMain,CULPRIT C,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys whispering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:01.04,DCMain,CULPRIT C,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:04.06,DCItalic,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. The clerk was working with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:05.55,DCMain,CULPRIT D,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:08.30,DCMain,CULPRIT D,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we get this started?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:11.86,DCItalic,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Just how many of them are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:14.80,DCMain,CULPRIT E,0000,0000,0000,,Quit dragging your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:16.22,DCMain,CULPRIT E,0000,0000,0000,,Walk quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:21.81,DCMain,CULPRIT D,0000,0000,0000,,How much more?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:24.09,DCMain,CULPRIT C,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like about 400-500 thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:29.60,DCMain,CULPRIT E,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody better make a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:35.45,DCItalic,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. We need to do something \Nabout these zip ties first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:40.86,DCItalic,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:46.43,DCItalic,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:49.88,DCItalic,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,By passing a shoelace through the ties, we can \Nuse the friction from rubbing against them to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:55.80,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Nice thinking, Furuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.72,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Help me untie the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:05.54,DCItalic,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,It's locked after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:09.25,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what are the culprits after?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:13.27,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Probably the ATM cash resupply.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:17.74,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,The resupply schedule is kept \Nsecret to prevent theft,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:23.25,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,but you can predict when it'll occur by checking \Nthe ATM's approximate balance on security images.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:24.80,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:27.64,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,So they couldn't have done \Nthis without the clerk's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.59,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:31.84,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why aren't they \Nconcealing their faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:35.08,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,The clerk wasn't even wearing sunglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:39.73,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,They may not intend to let their hostages \Nleave alive once they're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:43.73,DCMain,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I just came here to get water.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.82,DCMain,SOTOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,I came to get snacks for my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:48.73,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. We'll do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:56.07,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we need to come up \Nwith a way to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:57.70,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,A switchboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.23,DCItalic,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,This could work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:07.08,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I can see why Team Captain Date
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:10.07,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,would think his dad is a \Ncoward if that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:11.38,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:15.72,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he watched a police \Nofficer grovel before a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:19.20,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how he feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:23.68,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,When my dad was mistakenly \Narrested for murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:26.42,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,everyone called me the son of a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:29.23,Murderer,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(875,1)}Murderer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:29.23,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,It almost made me hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:34.90,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,In my case, I managed not to crack
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:37.30,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,because the guys at the gym told \Nme to believe in my dad and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:38.67,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.62,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,So, Morofushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:43.31,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:48.56,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,but if you tell us, our dumb advice \Nmight be able to help you in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:52.00,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Help...me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.13,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:57.36,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,No, look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:00.62,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,That convenience store's sign is flashing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:05.06,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,like Morse code.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:09.94,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute. That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:13.44,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,That's not like Morse code.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:16.51,DCMain,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:17.70,DCMain,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's being remodeled?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:23.71,Remodeling,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,960)}Remodeling in Progress \NWe're terribly sorry for any inconvenience
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:20.70,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll have to go to \Nanother convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:22.14,DCMain,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:28.08,DCMain,CULPRIT E,0000,0000,0000,,The security company car \Ncrossed the traffic light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:30.84,DCMain,CULPRIT E,0000,0000,0000,,Go take down the remodeling sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:31.96,DCMain,CULPRIT A,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:56.03,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:00.48,DCMain,HARIGAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, seriously? Isn't that a rifle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:05.41,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a wuss. It's obviously a replica \Nfor filming movies or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:10.42,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what movie are you guys \Nfilming? Let us be in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:13.11,DCItalic,CULPRIT D,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening? What's all that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:15.90,DCMain,CULPRIT B,0000,0000,0000,,Three strange men have entered the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:16.47,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'll be Tequila, some kind of police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:16.92,DCItalic,CULPRIT D,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:20.18,DCMain,CULPRIT D,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if it's just \Nthree of them. Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:23.06,DCMain,CHIEDA,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Are they really filming a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:24.93,DCMain,BETSUGI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god, I'm so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:30.01,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys. They said they'd let us be extras.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:37.11,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty noisy out there. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:39.40,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have kept you waiting, Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:40.53,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:43.03,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morofushi? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:48.40,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,We saw the sign's Morse code and \Ncame to take down the culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:50.04,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Not by force...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:52.70,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,But with numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:57.27,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,We're just doing what your dad tried to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:19:58.10,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.55,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Hagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:00.66,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:05.85,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, what my dad tried to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:09.90,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually at the convenience store
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:14.72,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,when your dad was beaten by that gangster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:17.86,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,You were there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:18.94,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:25.95,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,You were probably too distracted \Nby your bloodied dad to notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:30.25,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,but several of the men's accomplices \Nentered the store after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:31.92,DCItalic,MAN A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:33.96,DCItalic,MAN I,0000,0000,0000,,The cops are coming. Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:42.84,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad probably noticed his \Naccomplices were in a nearby car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:47.83,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he'd attempted to arrest him, \Nif his accomplices had joined the fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:49.47,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,he couldn't have beaten them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:53.53,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,If a fight broke out inside the store \Nor if they barricaded themselves inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:55.98,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,the other customers could've been harmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:21:00.01,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,There were a bunch of us in \Nthere at the time, like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:01.52,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,a pregnant woman, and an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:06.40,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,And since the police arrived so quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:09.19,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,your dad probably reported the crime
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:15.71,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,and was trying to keep him from going deeper \Ninto the store until the police arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.53,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,So, Team Leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:23.26,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,your dad wasn't begging for his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:31.91,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,It was his cop heart that refused to see \Nanyone get hurt that made him do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.88,0:23:07.85,DCItalic,DATE DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:09.90,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad. How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:11.62,DCMain,DATE DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:13.91,DCMain,DATE DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Why the sudden phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:17.21,DCMain,DATE DAD,0000,0000,0000,,What? There's someone you want me to meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:20.92,DCMain,DATE DAD,0000,0000,0000,,You're already that age, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:26.91,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already 22. You probably forgot \Nsince we haven't met in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.69,0:23:32.36,DCMain,DATE DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, how's the police academy going?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:34.43,DCMain,DATE DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Think you'll become a good cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:35.95,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.91,0:23:38.93,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Not as good as you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.01,0:23:41.97,DCItalic,DATE DAD,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
